      "parameters": {
        "color": 7,
        "width": 1488,
        "height": 928,
        "content": "# üí¨ OpenAI Chat Agent with Slack Listening\n\nThis workflow connects a chatbot to **Slack**.  \nIt listens to user messages, sends them to an **OpenAI agent**, and replies back in the same Slack channel.\n"
      },
